Package org.opencastproject.workflow.api

Class ConfiguredTagsAndFlavors

java.lang.Object
org.opencastproject.workflow.api.ConfiguredTagsAndFlavors
public class ConfiguredTagsAndFlavors extends Object
Class for Handling source/target tags and flavors. Consists of four lists each containing a number of configured source/target tags and flavors. Tags are stored as strings, while flavors ar stored as flavor objects.
